body:
Avengers Academy

Avengers Academy will be shut down. The players have time until Febuary to finish all stories, then the servers will be down.

It was my favourite mobile game and I’ve just bought Frost Giant Loki!

Frost Giant Loki looks great (he is also shirtless) and I will really miss fighting enemies with all my heroes (and villians/anti heroes/ midunderstood murderous cinnamon rolls)

body:
S2 Ep 4

Molly’s trust for Topher is because she strongly desires having a family and I’m sad because it does not look like it is going to end well.

Nico and Topher have great chemistry. I feel like all the actors have really gotten more opportunity to shine this season.

KAROLINA IS NICO’S FAVORITE DISNEY PRINCESS SHE SAID IT HERSELF FOLKS

Karolina you dumbass don’t go in the big hole with Jonah urghh. Like I understand this is an arc for her but it WILL end badly

35. Female. Social democrat. Agnostic. Critical (not gender critical) feminist. Pro-social justice, but anti-extremism. I am well aware that my race, sexual orientation, gender identity, and age offer me certain privileges, thank you very much.

I don't do trigger warnings. I can't keep track of everyone's triggers.

I mostly access the site on my mobile browser, so I won't always see notifications or IMs. I'm not ignoring anybody, I swear!

blog.name: markbrooksart

blog.description:
I'm a comic artist mostly for Marvel Comics but do/have done work for DC Comics, Darkhorse Comics, Warner Brothers, Disney, Lucas Film, and Hasbro from time to time.

2014 Inkpot award winner from San Diego Comic Con International. Father to Jack, husband to Lisa and feeding/poop slave to Gingerbread and Lulu.

I like to think I'm a swell guy but your mileage may vary.
